<!-- Troubleshooting Help --><div class="help-section"><nav class="help-breadcrumb"><a href="/help">Help</a> / <span>Troubleshooting</span></nav><h1><i class="fas fa-tools"></i> Troubleshooting</h1><p class="help-intro">Solutions to common issues.</p><div class="help-block"><h2>Application Won't Start</h2><ol><li>Check that .NET 10 Runtime is installed</li><li>Verify the database file exists and isn't corrupted</li><li>Check Windows Event Viewer for error messages</li><li>Try running as Administrator</li></ol></div><div class="help-block"><h2>Data Not Saving</h2><ul><li>Check disk space - database needs room to grow</li><li>Verify write permissions on database folder</li><li>Check if antivirus is blocking file writes</li></ul></div><div class="help-block"><h2>Reports Not Generating</h2><ul><li>Ensure date range has transactions</li><li>Check filters aren't excluding all data</li><li>Try a broader date range first</li></ul></div><div class="help-block"><h2>Slow Performance</h2><ul><li>Large databases (10,000+ transactions) may need optimization</li><li>Close other applications to free memory</li><li>Consider archiving old transactions</li></ul></div><div class="help-block"><h2>Dark Mode Not Working</h2><ol><li>Click the moon/sun icon in sidebar</li><li>Clear browser cache (if using web version)</li><li>Restart the application</li></ol></div><div class="help-block"><h2>Get More Help</h2><ul><li>Check the <a href="/help/faq">FAQ</a> for common questions</li><li>Review the <a href="/help/glossary">Glossary</a> for term definitions</li><li>Contact your system administrator</li></ul></div></div>
